# Copy to .env.local and adjust. Vite only exposes vars prefixed with VITE_.

# The app calls OpenF1 directly by default — free historical data (2023+) needs
# no key. For live real-time, add your key in the app under Settings → API Key.

# Optionally route through the caching proxy (keeps the key server-side and lets
# one key serve many viewers). Leave unset to call OpenF1 directly.
# VITE_OPENF1_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8787/v1

# ---- server/proxy.mjs (standalone Node proxy: npm run proxy) ----
# Your OpenF1 key — required for LIVE data through the proxy. Never commit a real key.
# OPENF1_API_KEY=your-key-here
# PORT=8787
# CACHE_TTL_MS=2000
